description:
&lt;p&gt;Are you a senior experienced procurement and stores technician looking to enhance your skills and move to the next level.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen in our senior technical leadership team. We need a dynamic leader for our procurement and distribution team to build on our current successes. Are you that person?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be expected to be the lead the team within the procurement and distribution team supporting, enabling and training staff to achieve high standards of patient care &amp; value for money for the trust. You will also support other senior technical staff in moving forward the technician agenda to improve our services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your skill set should include leadership, HR process and management, reporting, audit and investigation along with budgetary and business case development experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To talk to our current post holder or arrange a visit please contact Greg Edwards on: 01296 315280 or Duncan Cooke Deputy Director of Pharmacy Operational services on: 01296 316383&lt;/p&gt;
